"},{"pid":"e1e0b6f0a3416cb4648197593b1e64ffefaf1166","tid":168743,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84043f6a426e6f9308d5bb32b11b1faad275b7ea","tid":168743,"uid":20971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓除咗usj啲飛要買定，交通果啲卡係咪到時機場可以買哂，仲有咩要預先係香港買定？</blockquote><br />\n我上次去 usj都係係關西機場買<br />\n不過我冇買pass<br />\n<br />\nic卡我問朋友借左<br />\n下次去應該會買張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUsj唔買pass會唔會要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都諗緊買唔買pass<br />\n因為都幾貴<br />\n我四月尾去，會唔會好多人</blockquote><br />\n我上年2月尾去<br />\n我同女友都係為左哈利波特區而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩哂成個hp區行下睇下食下就走<br />\n前後都係4個鐘到<br />\n排4d果個就唔駛一個鐘"},{"pid":"8a123105cab4720d0b920098c48b3004687b2b69","tid":168743,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓除咗usj啲飛要買定，交通果啲卡係咪到時機場可以買哂，仲有咩要預先係香港買定？</blockquote><br />\n電話卡wifi egg<br />\n其實除左usj 冇野要買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對定錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家先對錢，會唔會好遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔去到用atm 禁</blockquote><br />\n去到用atm會抵過香港對定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc55e83e53cdc484c1547af6a82c87d5b3b419b","tid":168743,"uid":81220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓除咗usj啲飛要買定，交通果啲卡係咪到時機場可以買哂，仲有咩要預先係香港買定？</blockquote><br />\n我上次去 usj都係係關西機場買<br />\n不過我冇買pass<br />\n<br />\nic卡我問朋友借左<br />\n下次去應該會買張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUsj唔買pass會唔會要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都諗緊買唔買pass<br />\n因為都幾貴<br />\n我四月尾去，會唔會好多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我十二月頭平日去<br />\n幾個熱門遊戲都好多人 例如哈利波特要等180分鐘<br />\n睇到塊版個個都等100分鐘以上<br />\n拎住pass係側邊入完全唔洗排咁經過晒啲排緊隊既人真係好爽<br />\n想玩得舒服就唔好慳個三百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買4款個個最抵"},{"pid":"a35465b86362739796e986256073587d8dd5051f","tid":168743,"uid":30540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問吓除咗usj啲飛要買定，交通果啲卡係咪到時機場可以買哂，仲有咩要預先係香港買定？</blockquote><br />\n我上次去 usj都係係關西機場買<br />\n不過我冇買pass<br />\n<br />\nic卡我問朋友借左<br />\n下次去應該會買張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUsj唔買pass會唔會要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都諗緊買唔買pass<br />\n因為都幾貴<br />\n我四月尾去，會唔會好多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我十二月頭平日去<br />\n幾個熱門遊戲都好多人 例如哈利波特要等180分鐘<br />\n睇到塊版個個都等100分鐘以上<br />\n拎住pass係側邊入完全唔洗排咁經過晒啲排緊隊既人真係好爽<br />\n想玩得舒服就唔好慳個三百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買4款個個最抵</blockquote><br />\n7款啦慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc39b865fa9d6b1a964b0904f271d9c482a8036","tid":168743,"uid":5327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"Fast pass要買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90565c9f11ded2d68e327fa691dfc04baa45c766","tid":168743,"uid":8766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:47:30.000Z","msg":"上次去USJ <br />\n前一日先上網買飛<br />\n無買fast pass玩到hp同飛天翼龍<br />\nHp仲要只係排40分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}